<br>
Look at that compared to the mage epic.  If the cleric epic is a delicious 3 scoop ice cream cone for guilds our epic is a chocolate cover &quot;poop-sickle&quot;.  The general feeling is &quot;what? give the mage another pet? so what..!  I want to rez'd in faster..&quot;  But they certainly came up with a nice bottle neck for us.  3 day rare spawns in a planar zone and then a random drop on the 7th isle of Air.  I bet you every mage that wanted an epic would have one if you had to go to the 8th isle for the cleric epic.  In fact, that is what they should have done.  Place cleric epic on 8th isle and ever other classes on a previous isle before that.. Problem solved.  we could all get our epic while the guilds mindless plows to get the clerics theirs.<br>
